---
---

<section class="manifesto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label-row">
      <p class="section-label">
        <span class="num">01</span>
        <span>Manifesto</span>
      </p>
      <hr class="rule flex-1" />
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto-grid">
      <h2 class="display">
        Your documents.<br/>
        Your infrastructure.<br/>
        <em class="italic-accent">Your rules.</em>
      </h2>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Every contract, invoice, and form in your business contains data worth extracting. But the tools that extract it expect you to hand your data over — to their cloud, their servers, their terms of service.
        </p>
        <p>
          Koji doesn't work that way. It runs on your infrastructure. It uses the models you choose. It shows you exactly what it's doing. And it's open source, forever.
        </p>
        <p class="signature">
          — The thing we wished existed when we needed it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    padding: var(--section-pad) 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .label-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .flex-1 { flex: 1; }

  .manifesto-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .manifesto h2 {
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .italic-accent {
    color: var(--vermillion);
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 100;
  }

  .prose {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 48ch;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }

  .prose p:first-child::first-line {
    font-variant: small-caps;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .signature {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .manifesto-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
